class Cat {
  private _x: number;
  private _y: number;

  constructor(x: number, y: number) {
    this._x = x
    this._y = y
  }
  // 访问器修饰器
  @dec(true)
  get  x() { return this._x }
  @dec(false)
  get  y() { return this._y }
}
```


### 属性修饰器

属性修饰器只有前两个参数
